The worst thing is that
we'll change jobs.

647
00:30:45,800 --> 00:30:47,420
Maybe there's a third option.

648
00:30:47,560 --> 00:30:48,730
We won't be the good guys.

649
00:30:48,730 --> 00:30:50,150
We won't be the bad guys either.

