680
00:32:07,320 --> 00:32:08,160
What do you mean?

681
00:32:08,180 --> 00:32:08,990
You should interview

682
00:32:08,990 --> 00:32:10,610
GM Zhao Ming
from the Finance Department.

683
00:32:10,610 --> 00:32:12,040
His name is in a different character.

684
00:32:12,040 --> 00:32:13,320
But you interviewed

685
00:32:13,320 --> 00:32:15,080
the GM of Zhonghe Financing.

686
00:32:15,080 --> 00:32:16,490
He's another person.

687
00:32:16,490 --> 00:32:18,000
Now, Mr. Zhao of the Finance Department

688
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,730
has boarded the plane to the U.S.

689
00:32:19,730 --> 00:32:21,990
He can't pick up calls
for the next 10 hours.

690
00:32:22,840 --> 00:32:23,700
Hold on...

691
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:34,750
Did the three of you set me up?

692
00:32:35,650 --> 00:32:36,840
