806
00:37:52,810 --> 00:37:53,810
Lead us by doing nothing.

807
00:37:54,070 --> 00:37:55,370
We won't bother you.

808
00:37:55,370 --> 00:37:56,290
We'll respect you

809
00:37:56,290 --> 00:37:57,850
in front of Manager Hu

810
00:37:57,850 --> 00:37:59,180
and the others.

811
00:37:59,790 --> 00:38:02,300
We'll give you credit for our work.

812
00:38:02,520 --> 00:38:03,810
We'll just get along

813
00:38:03,810 --> 00:38:05,620
