815
00:38:14,450 --> 00:38:15,740
Bye, Mr. Ma.

816
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:28,550
Wait a moment.

817
00:38:34,640 --> 00:38:35,480
Thanks.

818
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:40,620
Mr. Ma, don't forget
to turn off the lights.

819
00:39:12,490 --> 00:39:14,770
Xiuya, I think you've really changed.

820
00:39:14,770 --> 00:39:16,850
You're no longer the girl

821
00:39:16,850 --> 00:39:17,910
who tolerates everything.

822
00:39:19,080 --> 00:39:22,740
I see things in a new light now.

823
00:39:24,010 --> 00:39:24,850
Great.

824
00:39:25,770 --> 00:39:27,160
Come on. Let's have breakfast.

